snippet: Atlético Madrid ended a 14-year winless run against Real Madrid to capture the Copa del Rey title, rallying to win in extra time.
abstract: Atletico Madrid ends 14-year winless run against Real Madrid to capture Copa del Rey title, rallying to win, 2-1, in extra time.
lead_paragraph: Atlético Madrid ended a 14-year winless run against Real Madrid to capture the Copa del Rey title, rallying to win in extra time.

headline.seo: Atlético Madrid Beats Real Madrid to Capture Copa del Rey Title
headline.main: Atlético Madrid Tops Real Madrid to Win Copa del Rey Title
